        "localization": {
          "name": "Dual Toxins",
          "description": "The first time this skill is activated while on the battlefield, the user will get the next turn by having their TU reduced to 0.\n\nTargets 2 enemies. If they are not burning, poisoned, or sleeping, they are randomly granted either Noxious Sleep for 100TU or Mega Poison for 200TU. \n\nNoxious Sleep can be applied repeatedly to units that have already slept while on the battlefield, and will not end from damage. A unit with Noxious Sleep will be granted Mega Poison for 200TU when Noxious Sleep expires.\n\nMega Poison deals 20 times the damage of normal Poison and cannot be overwritten by normal Poison or Super Poison. These status effects will overwrite other status effects if applied.",
          "selected": "Grants 2 enemies Noxious Sleep or Mega Poison\n(May overwrite other status effects)"
        }
      },
