          "name": "Final Vows",
          "description": "250% damage to 1 enemy, 400% if there is any poisoned or sleeping enemy on the battlefield, or 600% damage if there are both (even if the target is not poisoned or sleeping). If the targeted enemy is not burning, poisoned, or sleeping, they are randomly granted either Noxious Sleep for 100TU or Mega Poison for 200TU.\n\nThese status effects will overwrite other status effects if applied. This attack ignores enemy damage reduction effects, Skin passive skills and the Counter Stance status effect. This is considered a Dream Hunter type Active Skill. This skill becomes locked for 50TU after use.",
